title: "Cicero: The open-source AI voice receptionist for law firms"
abstract: "Cicero is an open-source AI voice receptionist for law firms: a talking website widget plus an inbound and outbound phone agent that answers, qualifies leads and books consultations to your calendar 24/7. Self-hosted, MIT licensed, set up by Claude in minutes."
